{"tid":2027154,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Epic商城免費送《GTA V》，結果作弊玩家在線上模式群魔亂舞","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:54:22.000Z","uid":193642,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1509edc615853e60c7accc23040d70b80091778a","tid":2027154,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/43198/hackers-take-full-advantage-of-gta-online-going-free?fbclid=IwAR12uchlFWiqgEE9sfyk_NMyxPzFWxO3jTLEux2f5KcgOuuasnKAGtVXtnA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F43198%2Fhackers-take-full-advantage-of-gta-online-going-free%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR12uchlFWiqgEE9sfyk_NMyxPzFWxO3jTLEux2f5KcgOuuasnKAGtVXtnA&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=28344d52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/43198/hackers-take-full-advantage-of-gta-online-going-free?fbclid=IwAR12uchlFWiqgEE9sfyk_NMyxPzFWxO3jTLEux2f5KcgOuuasnKAGtVXtnA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在 Epic Games 商城大送《俠盜獵車手 5》（Grand Theft Auto V；GTA5）後，再度為這款發售多年的大作注入活水，但免費的同時也讓作弊玩家沒有損失遊戲的風險，因而原本就有的外掛、模組玩家更是肆無忌憚的在線上模式《GTA Online》群魔亂舞。<br />\n<br />\n已經有不少玩家在 Reddit 、Twitter 等網路社群抱怨，由於本月的《GTA Online》玩家自組了外星人戰爭的遊戲，原本這是個很好的點子，但自從免費週開始以來，大量的作弊玩家開始入侵，有人搞出了上百架飛機癱瘓了伺服器，有人把籠子丟去了玩家大廳，讓其他玩家被關在籠子內無法移動。<br />\n<br />\n誇張一點的，有人在 Reddit 分享了一張他看到有玩家用坦克和飛機組出了一台超大型機器人。而更糟的是不光如此，有玩家回報即便他是在單人模式（但有連結 Rockstar 伺服器）的情況下，作弊玩家居然可以利用漏洞跑進他的世界把他幹掉。<br />\n<br />\n不可否認的是《GTA Online》中，這些使用外掛的作弊玩家是一直存在的，但在免費週末後，這些人的人數不但有增加的趨勢，作法也更是肆無忌憚。因此玩家想玩到正常一點的 GTA，可能得等到免費期間結束，並在官方開始對這些玩家動手後才能有所緩解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾錢Epic買GTA嘅玩家陰公囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36ed410f3c25112c00f4180d7a83547e01d246c","tid":2027154,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"有玩家回報即便他是在單人模式（但有連結 Rockstar 伺服器）的情況下，作弊玩家居然可以利用漏洞跑進他的世界把他幹掉。<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪唔識整game架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2b1b5babaf5e61b5613a51269bf41687958519","tid":2027154,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e36ed410f3c25112c00f4180d7a83547e01d246c","tid":2027154,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"有玩家回報即便他是在單人模式（但有連結 Rockstar 伺服器）的情況下，作弊玩家居然可以利用漏洞跑進他的世界把他幹掉。<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪唔識整game架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁癲"},{"pid":"07f803f394c0f4bef82f20af39b27b87e56cdfb5","tid":2027154,"uid":220766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2b1b5babaf5e61b5613a51269bf41687958519","tid":2027154,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e36ed410f3c25112c00f4180d7a83547e01d246c","tid":2027154,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"有玩家回報即便他是在單人模式（但有連結 Rockstar 伺服器）的情況下，作弊玩家居然可以利用漏洞跑進他的世界把他幹掉。<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪唔識整game架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁癲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110a58aeb8163317bdde3889a004cf52d4c0d38f","ti